ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

The Employee Management System is a simple and clean backend-focused web application developed using Spring Boot.
It provides core CRUD operations (Create, Read, Delete) for managing employee data through RESTful APIs, with a minimal HTML page only for basic interaction.

This project is designed to demonstrate Java, Spring Boot, and REST API skills, making it ideal for GitHub portfolios and interviews.

