| ------ | ------------------- | --------------------- |
| GET    | `/employees`        | Application status    |
| POST   | `/employees/add`    | Add new employee      |
| GET    | `/employees/all`    | View all employees    |
| POST   | `/employees/delete` | Delete employee by ID |

